cc:Work.dc:title: Box - StevensonScreenBox
cc:Work.dc:description:
A box with Stevenson Screens front and back.
This box is intended to hold a simple weather station.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes StevensonScreenBox Command line short: boxes StevensonScreenBox
